      <title>麦莉（Milei）收取$ 20,000参加私人晚餐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/milei-charged-20-000-to-attend-private-dinners-as-congressman</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当哈维尔·米利（Javier Milei）与他的客人坐在布宜诺斯艾利斯（Buenos Aires）的豪华摩天大楼（Le Parc）的22楼时，已经收集了现金。厚厚的一百美元账单，总计约20,000美元，塞在他的姐姐和业务经理卡琳娜·米利（Karina Milei）的袋子里。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/milei-charged-20-000-to-attend-private-dinners-as-congressman</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰计划提高国防支出和退出地雷禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/finland-to-raise-defense-spending-target-to-3-of-gdp-by-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰总理佩特里·奥尔波（Petteri Orpo）说，到2029年，芬兰政府计划将该国的国防支出提高到其经济产出的3％，以应对更具侵略性的俄罗斯风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/finland-to-raise-defense-spending-target-to-3-of-gdp-by-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 11:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的制药威胁将关税纳入未知领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-tariffs-pharmaceutical-industry-levies-threaten-major-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三十年来，一项旨在改善挽救生命的药物的世界贸易组织协议，保护了制药行业免受关税的保护。]]></description>
